title: Bounding box prediction using Faster RCNN Resnet
description: This is a baseline kernel, the purpose of this kernel to provide the insight of the competition. It is using Faster RCNN Inception Resnet v2 pretrained model on Old Open Image Dataset that contains 545 classes similar to New Open Image Dataset. I have done some analysis between old and new dataset's classes, checkout this kernel. I have used Model Zoo's utility files for object detection purpose.
